text: Olivia Frances Culpo (born May 8, 1992) is an American model, reality television and social media personality, former beauty pageant title holder and actress. After winning the Miss Rhode Island USA competition, she went on to be crowned Miss USA, and then Miss Universe in 2012. She was born in Cranston, Rhode Island. On June 29, 2024, Culpo married professional football player Christian McCaffrey. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Miss Universe winners Category:Businesspeople from Rhode Island Category:American television personalities Category:American movie actors Category:American Internet celebrities Category:Actors from Rhode Island Category:People from Cranston, Rhode Island Category:Miss USA
